    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "Alcohol is a common substance available in stunning variety. The Price of a dose of alcohol depends on the specific beverage. You can\u2019t recover from the sickened condition from alcohol while affected.  \n   \n If you fail a saving throw against alcohol other than initial saves, the affliction\u2019s stage doesn\u2019t increase; the only way to increase the stage of alcohol\u2019s affliction is to consume more alcohol.",
        "level": 0,
        "traits": [
